flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Receive User Input]
    B --> C["Embed User Query<br/>via Vector Model"]
    C --> D["Search Archive<br/>Top-1 Semantic Match"]
    D --> E["Load Short-Term Window<br/>Last 3 Exchanges"]
    E --> F["Build LLM Context<br/>Window + Archive Hit"]
    F --> G[Call LLM]
    G --> H[Generate Response]
    H --> I[Display Response to User]
    I --> J["Append Exchange<br/>to Short-Term Window"]
    J --> K{Window Full?}
    K -->|Yes| L["Evict Oldest Exchange<br/>Embed + Archive It"]
    K -->|No| M[Keep Window As-Is]
    L --> N{Continue Chat?}
    M --> N
    N -->|Yes| B
    N -->|No| O([End])